      <title>朝鲜黑客入侵两家韩国芯片齿轮制造商</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/north-korean-hackers-two-south-korean-chip-equipment-firms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[首尔情报机构周一表示，自去年以来，平壤支持的网络攻击者已渗透到两家韩国半导体设备公司，可能窃取国内芯片制造项目的情报。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/north-korean-hackers-two-south-korean-chip-equipment-firms</guid>
